bolt port (high-speed data and video output).\n- Two USB 3.0 ports (up to 5 Gbps).\n- SDXC card slot for easy photo/video transfers.\n- FireWire 800 and Gigabit Ethernet ports.\n- Built-in SuperDrive (8x DVD/CD writer).\n- Camera: 720p FaceTime HD camera for clear video calls.\n- Audio: Stereo speakers with subwoofer and omnidirectional microphone.\n- Battery: Built-in 63.5-watt-hour lithium-polymer battery (up to 7 hours of wireless web).",
