      "categoryId": "cat1",
      "title": "GM19P Mouse",
      "description": "RGB BACKLIT GAMING MOUSE\\nCool looking and designed for gaming. Streamlined design enhances grip. 12000dpi high-resolution optical sensor, the resolution can be changed by driver software. Backlight and additional keys allow you to enjoy the convenience of control in any game. Gaming sensors work on any surface. The DPI change button lets you adjust the speed of mouse movement, and a color indicator reminds you which settings are currently in use. The button design on the left can help you move forward or backward quickly, improving efficiency.\\n\\nHardware Upgrade\\nUpgraded 12000 DPI optical engine, using high-performance sensors, the control is stable and precise, and the movements are flexible and free to meet your precise positioning requirements.\\n\\nRGB Circulation Backlit\\nThe 122(±5g) ultra-lightweight honeycomb shell design the mouse very lightweight and convenient to use. and it helps keep the paint dry.\\n\\nThe Soft Rubber Scroll Wheel\\nThe mouse is designed with a soft rubber wheel, which is soft and skin-friendly, and will not hurt your hands for a long time.\\n\\nErgonomic Design\\nGaming temperament ergonomic design for right hands\\n\\n12000 DPI Optical Engine\\nUsing high-performance sensors, the control is smooth and precise, and the movement is flexible and free to meet your precise positioning requirements.\\n\\nErgonomic Design\\nThe non-slip rubber pads for buttons are included in the box, which can be freely replaced according to personal preferences. The replacement is simple and convenient.\\n\\nSupport Marco Programming\\nAbout 16.8 million colors can be customized intelligent RGB lighting, personality shine.\\n\\nUSB Braided Cable\\nThe braid on the wire often prolongs its life, and protects not only from bending, but also from such phenomena as the teeth of your beloved cat or the playful hands of your younger brother.\\n\\n6D Soft-touch Plastic\\nThe mouse has a pleasant, matte finish, which makes it not only pleasant to the touch, but also does not allow it to slip out of your hand at the wrong moment, even if it sweats after long battles. And if you have a wet wipe nearby, then the traces will be erased in an instant.\\n\\nPlug & Play\\nThe mouse works autonomously and without the need to install additional software. When connected to a computer via a USB port, you can be up and running in seconds.",
