      "categoryId": "cat1",
      "title": "GM23 Mouse",
      "description": "RGB Circulation Backlit Gaming Mouse\\n\\nGM23 features an RGB circulation backlit gaming temperament ergonomic design for right hands. The DPI is adjustable to meet the needs of all kinds of games.\\n\\nRGB LIGHT GAMING MOUSE\\nCool looking and designed for gaming. Streamlined design enhances grip. It has a 12800dpi high-resolution optical sensor, with resolution adjustable via driver software. Backlight and additional keys allow for convenient control in any game. Gaming sensors work on any surface. The DPI change button lets you adjust the speed of mouse movement, and a color indicator reminds you which settings are currently in use. The button design on the left can help you move forward or backward quickly, improving efficiency.\\n\\nRGB circulation Backlit\\nGM23 lighting changes depending on the DPI mode you choose. Thanks to this, you will never be mistaken about which mode is being used right now.\\n\\nLightweight gaming mouse\\nClassic black and white 2 colors to choose from, to better meet your diverse needs.\\n\\n3D non-slip roller\\nThe mouse is designed with a soft rubber wheel, which is soft and skin-friendly, and will not hurt your hands for a long time.\\n\\nRemovable counterweight\\nGM23 can be weighted for optimal feel by adding counterweights. The product comes with an 18g counterweight set.\\n\\nTwo Colors Available\\nGM23 is available in black and white, both equipped with dazzling lighting effects that fit both the minimalist and gaming crowd.\\n\\n12800 DPI optical engine\\nUsing high-performance sensors, the control is smooth and precise, and the movement is flexible and free to meet your precise positioning requirements.\\n\\nHigh-Quality Switch\\nUsing high-quality keys, the service life can reach millions of clicks, the sound is crisp, the response is sensitive, and the frequent use is not stuck.\\n\\nSupport Marco Programming\\nAbout 16.8 million colors can be customized intelligent RGB lighting, personality shine.\\n\\nSupport to All Popular Games\\nOptimized the response rate for the popular games, Combine with 8 grade DPI, make the DPI switching more precise and more enjoy the games.\\n\\nMatte soft-touch plastic\\nThe mouse has a pleasant, matte finish, which makes it not only pleasant to the touch, but also does not allow it to slip out of your hand at the wrong moment, even if it sweats after long battles. And if you have a wet wipe nearby, then the traces will be erased in an instant.\\n\\nPlug & Play\\nThe mouse works autonomously and without the need to install additional software. When connected to a computer via a USB port, you can be up and running in seconds.",
      "price": 19.99,
      "originalPrice": 19.99,
      "salePrice": 19.99,
