      "description": "Introducing the Dazzling Gaming Mouse GM22, a pro gaming optical mouse with a unique shape specially designed for games. Its streamlined design enhances grip, providing comfort during extended gaming sessions. The mouse features a 4800dpi high-resolution optical sensor, with adjustable resolution via driver software. Enjoy vibrant RGB circulation backlighting that changes with your chosen DPI mode, ensuring you always know your current settings. Additional keys and a convenient side button allow for quick forward/backward movement, improving efficiency in any game. The gaming sensor works on any surface, and the mouse supports Marco Programming for customizable intelligent RGB lighting. Optimized for popular games, the GM22 offers smooth and precise control with its high-performance sensor. It's a plug-and-play device, requiring no additional software installation, making it ready to use in seconds.",
