      "title": "GM80 Mouse",
      "description": "The Transformers Gaming Mouse (GM80) features a mecha shape design with a cool appearance, adjustable to fit different palm sizes for enhanced grip. It boasts a 4000dpi high-resolution optical sensor, which can be adjusted via driver software. The mouse includes colorful RGB backlighting and additional programmable keys for convenient control in any game. Its gaming sensors work on any surface, and a dedicated DPI change button allows for on-the-fly speed adjustments with a color indicator for current settings. The left-side buttons are designed for fast forward/rewind functions, boosting efficiency. The unique mecha-style design adds to the gaming atmosphere, and it comes with high polymer wear-resisting foot pads, 10 times stronger than normal ones. It supports Marco Programming with 16.8 million customizable RGB colors and is optimized for popular games with 8-grade DPI switching for precise control. This plug-and-play mouse works autonomously without additional software, connecting via USB for immediate use.",
