      "id": "prod_1775215897655wi0c3b",
      "sellerId": "exshopi_official",
      "storeId": "exshopi_official",
      "categoryId": "cat1",
      "title": "BTM011 Mouse",
      "description": "Experience unparalleled freedom and customization with the DIY Wireless Gaming Mouse! With an incredibly lightweight design of only 72g, this game-changing mouse allows for effortless disassembly and customization. Swap out the backplate, microswitches, and custom pressure sensors to build your one-of-a-kind gaming mouse. With ultra-fast wireless connectivity, aerodynamic design, and rugged durability, get the competitive edge you need to dominate the game. The DIY Wireless Gaming Mouse is the ultimate gaming accessory that empowers gamers to build and customize a mouse that fits their unique style and preferences. Order yours today and elevate your gaming experience like never before!\\n\\nDetachable Without Tools\\nThe mouse can be disassembled by hand without tools, which is convenient for understanding the internal structure of the mouse and DIYing a mouse that suits your own feel.\\n\\n12000 DPI Optical Engine\\nUsing high-performance sensors, the control is smooth and precise, and the movement is flexible and free to meet your precise positioning requirements.\\n\\nErgonomic Design\\nThe non-slip rubber pads for buttons are included in the box, which can be freely replaced according to personal preferences. The replacement is simple and convenient.\\n\\nSupport Marco Programming\\nAbout 16.8 million colors can be customized intelligent RGB lighting, personality shine.\\n\\n6D Soft-touch Plastic\\nThe mouse has a pleasant, matte finish, which makes it not only pleasant to the touch, but also does not allow it to slip out of your hand at the wrong moment, even if it sweats after long battles. And if you have a wet wipe nearby, then the traces will be erased in an instant.",
      "price": 19.99,
