    {
      "id": "prod_1775215897655a8yrvq",
      "sellerId": "exshopi_official",
      "storeId": "exshopi_official",
      "categoryId": "cat1",
      "title": "MK009 Pro Keyboard",
      "description": "The MK009 Pro Floating Mechanical Keyboard is designed with ergonomic features for ultimate comfort during extended typing sessions. Its full 104-key anti-ghosting layout ensures every keystroke is registered seamlessly, making it ideal for gamers and professionals. The keyboard features durable dual-injected ABS keycaps and a stylish metal matte panel, ensuring longevity and a premium look. Users can customize their typing experience with hot-swappable switches and enjoy a smooth, linear feel with red mechanical switches, which have a lifespan of approximately 50 million keystrokes. The intuitive control knob allows for quick and easy volume adjustment, while the detachable Type-C cable provides versatile connectivity. Enhance productivity with macro driver settings for customizable key zones and illuminate your workspace with stunning RGB lighting offering 18 different effects. The MK009 Pro combines style, functionality, and durability for an exceptional typing experience.",
