    {
      "id": "prod_1775215897655avj4f0",
      "sellerId": "exshopi_official",
      "storeId": "exshopi_official",
      "categoryId": "cat1",
      "title": "BTK011 Keyboard",
      "description": "The BTK011 is a 97-key DIY wireless mechanical keyboard kit featuring a customized PCB, Mac & Windows double layout, and gasket-mount design. It includes silicone spacers, a sandwich silicone silencer, a custom stabilizer, and a silicone pad at the bottom to enhance typing sound. The keyboard is equipped with RGB SMD lighting for a cool gaming experience and a multi-layer silent structure with Poron sandwich layer and slow-rebound bottom case foam for a soft and smooth typing experience. It also features pre-lubed stabilizers and switch pads for enriched performance. The full keys anti-ghosting ensures a smooth gaming experience, and the detachable USB-C cable makes it portable and customizable.",
