      "title": "HP099 Headset",
      "description": "The HP099 gaming headset features virtual 7.1 surround sound technology, delivering 360° spatial audio for precise sound positioning, ensuring you dominate every battlefield detail. Equipped with 50mm large drivers, high-magnetic cores, and ultra-thin diaphragms, it offers powerful bass and rich audio layers. The high-sensitivity omnidirectional noise-cancelling microphone ensures clear communication, while the large, skin-friendly earcups guarantee superior noise isolation and long-lasting comfort. The lightweight, durable metal frame with a self-adjusting elastic headband fits seamlessly, while the dynamic RGB lighting enhances the gaming atmosphere. With multifunctional inline controls for easy volume, lighting, and microphone adjustments, and three classic colors to choose from, the HP099 combines style and performance to be the ultimate choice for gamers!",
