ugged in and bent, so you can store it and enjoy listening.\\n\\nErgonomic Comfort Designed for Endless Wear\\nThe representative of comfortable ergonomics, long-term wearing without pressure! The optimized ergonomic design ensures stability and comfort, allowing your ears to listen freely. The soft and breathable mesh headband, sports mesh and memory foam earmuffs fit perfectly. The headband is retractable and adjustable, and the ear shells are light and flippable, bringing an all-round comfortable experience.\\n\\nPower-Packed Performance Battery\\nBuilt-in 1200mAh battery, up to 45 hours of battery life, so you don't have to worry about battery life.\\n\\nClassic Black and White Headset\\nTwo-color options, a perfect combination of function and fashion, suitable for any occasion.",
