    {
      "id": "prod_1775215897656bj6r18",
      "sellerId": "exshopi_official",
      "storeId": "exshopi_official",
      "categoryId": "cat1",
      "title": "CO015 Combo",
      "description": "The CO015 4-in-1 package combination is specially designed for games. It includes a USB one-handed keyboard with color backlight and full key anti-ghosting. The mouse features a honeycomb hollow design, making it lightweight and comfortable for extended gaming sessions. Its 6400DPI high-resolution light sensor ensures precise tracking and quick response. The DPI change button allows for on-the-fly adjustment of mouse speed. The adapter seamlessly connects input devices to various consoles like PS3/PS4/N-Switch/X-ONE/X-360. The mouse pad has a smooth cloth surface for optimal operation and a non-slip bottom. The CO015 package is a comprehensive solution to enhance your gaming experience.",
      "price": 19.99,
      "originalPrice": 19.99,
