      "categoryId": "cat1",
      "title": "M390 Mouse",
      "description": "The M390 wired office vertical mouse is ergonomically designed to keep the user's palm in a near-vertical position, reducing arm fatigue often associated with traditional mice. Its exquisite micro-grinding technology provides a comfortable and delicate texture. The mouse features adjustable DPI settings (800-1200-2400-3200) to suit various scenarios and is plug-and-play via a USB interface. It is made from environmentally friendly and durable ABS plastic. Additional features include volume control buttons for easy adjustment and a matte soft-touch plastic finish that ensures a comfortable grip even during prolonged use.",
