    {
      "id": "prod_1775215897656kuvaaf",
      "sellerId": "exshopi_official",
      "storeId": "exshopi_official",
      "categoryId": "cat1",
      "title": "R380 Mouse",
      "description": "R380 wireless office vertical mouse, \"vertical\" refers to the vertical state where the palm of the user is close to the desktop when the user uses the mouse. In the process of using an ordinary mouse, the user's arm moves laterally to control it, and it is easy to cause arm fatigue for a long time. Thanks to its ergonomic design, it is comfortable to hold and the arm is naturally perpendicular to the mouse, which will serve you for a long time. The surface of the mouse adopts exquisite micro-grinding technology, which is comfortable and delicate to the touch. Suitable for office, home, outdoor leisure and entertainment, etc., it can easily cope with various occasions, and the comfortable and soft touch coating will make you happy for a long time. The mouse DPI is adjustable, 800-1200-1600 respectively, and the USB interface is plug and play.\\n\\nABS Plastic Shell\\nThe mouse is designed with ABS environmental protection material, which is environmentally friendly and durable.\\n\\nErgonomic design\\nStreamlined shape, fashionable ergonomic design, fit and feel comfortable!\\n\\nAdjustable DPI switch\\n800-1200-1600 3-level DPI can meet a variety of scenarios.\\n\\n2.4G wireless\\n2.4G wireless mouse, the transmission distance is 10 meters, get rid of the trouble of data cable entanglement.\\n\\nMatte soft-touch plastic\\nThe mouse has a pleasant matte finish that is not only comfortable to the touch but also won't slip out of your hands even after prolonged use. And if you have wet wipes nearby, the traces will be wiped off in an instant.\\n\\nPlug & Play\\nThe mouse works autonomously and without the need to install additional software. When connected to a computer via a USB port, you can be up and running in seconds.",
      "price": 19.99,
      "originalPrice": 19.99,
      "salePrice": 19.99,
      "image": "https://www.meetion.com/lifisher-1660535604521/png80-t3-scale100.webp",
