      "description": "The R390 is a wireless office vertical mouse designed for ergonomic comfort. Its \"vertical\" design allows the user's palm to remain close to the desktop, reducing arm fatigue often associated with traditional mice. The mouse features an exquisite micro-grinding process for a comfortable and delicate hand feel. It includes quick volume adjustment buttons and is suitable for various occasions such as office, home, and outdoor leisure. The mouse DPI is adjustable (800-1200-2400-3200), and the USB transmitter offers plug-and-play functionality.",
