    {
      "id": "prod_17752158976567lnomr",
      "sellerId": "exshopi_official",
      "storeId": "exshopi_official",
      "categoryId": "cat1",
      "title": "M359 Mouse",
      "description": "The M359 wired office mouse is ideal for those who use the palm or fingers to hold it. It fits in the hand like a glove thanks to its ergonomic design and extra space for the ring and pinky fingers. The upper cover of the mouse adopts an exquisite matte process, which is comfortable in hand and delicate in texture. Suitable for office, home, outdoor leisure and entertainment, etc., it can easily cope with many occasions, and the comfortable soft touch coating will make you happy for a long time. The USB interface is plug and play and can serve you for a long time.\\n\\nPortable and lightweight\\nSimple and lightweight shape, classic curved line design, make your desktop simpler and better office.\\n\\nFrosted surface\\nThe upper cover of the mouse adopts a delicate frosting process, which is comfortable to the hand and delicate in texture.\\n\\nAnti-skid wheel\\nMouse wheel gear design, non-slip and sweat-proof, comfortable to use!\\n\\nUSB Line length 1.5 meters\\nThe standard mouse cable is 1.5 meters, which can meet your needs for office and home.\\n\\nMatte soft-touch plastic\\nThe mouse has a pleasant matte finish that is not only comfortable to the touch but also won't slip out of your hands even after prolonged use. And if you have wet wipes nearby, the traces will be wiped off in an instant.\\n\\nPlug & Play\\nThe mouse works autonomously and without the need to install additional software. When connected to a computer via a USB port, you can be up and running in seconds.",
