      "description": "The BTM002 wireless office mouse, wireless and Bluetooth dual mode (Bluetooth dual channel) is compact, easy to carry and suitable for everyone. The side of the mouse has a non-slip texture to prevent fingers from slipping due to sweat. The use of a new generation of low-power energy-saving technology, more energy saving, conducive to environmental protection. The overall lightweight design makes the mouse only 75 grams, built-in rechargeable battery, TYPE-C charging port charging, full of a charge can be used for 1-3 months. Mouse color is rich, there are 5 colors to choose from: black, white, gradual pink, gradual purple, khaki. Feel comfortable, fine texture. There are 3 DPI options, colorful LED lights. Whether you are in a quiet office, studying in the library, or working late at night, it will create a comfortable environment for you. USB interface plug and play, can serve you for a long time.",
