      "description": "The K200 USB standard wired keyboard features an ergonomic design and a high-quality membrane. It is waterproof with several drainage holes at the bottom, allowing liquids to drain out easily if accidentally spilled. This ensures continued use after wiping it clean. The comfortable mute buttons provide a quiet typing experience, suitable for various environments like offices, libraries, or late-night work. Its standard full-size layout with 104/105 keys meets diverse office input requirements, and the UV process for key characters ensures durability and a longer service life. The keyboard is plug-and-play via its USB interface, making it ready for use in seconds without additional software installation.",
