      "description": "The BTK001 Bluetooth folding keyboard is small, portable, and easy to carry, fitting effortlessly into handbags and pockets. Its ergonomic design meets the demands of business office use, significantly improving operational efficiency and ensuring a longer service life. The comfortable mute button creates a quiet environment, whether in a busy office, a library, or working late at night. Suitable for various occasions like office, home, and outdoor recreation, it offers a comfortable soft-touch coating for prolonged use. It features fast Bluetooth connection with laptops, tablets, mobile phones, and desktop computers with Bluetooth modules. Available in black, white, purple, and pink, it is designed for long-term service.",
