      "description": "The AT100 wired keyboard and mouse set features an ergonomic design and UV printing process for the character surface, making it suitable for business office needs. It aims to greatly improve operation efficiency and ensure a longer service life. The mouse has a DPI of 1000, catering to business office requirements. It is designed to create a comfortable environment whether in a quiet office, library, or working late at night. This combo is suitable for office, home, outdoor leisure, and entertainment, easily adapting to various occasions. The comfortable and soft-touch coating provides a pleasant experience for extended periods. The USB interface offers plug-and-play functionality for long-term use.",
